          <div>
              <p><em>Information security</em> is the practice of protecting information in an information system from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, disruption, modification, or destruction.
              This section is a growing recollection of single articles on information security which - at some point - will be converted into a book at some point.</p>
              <p>Find out more under <a href='@{siteAddress}/information-security/'>@{siteAddress}/information-security/</a></p>
         </div>
